<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GuardianAgent - GitHub Integration Setup</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS v4 via CDN -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background-color: #EAEAEA;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#EAEAEA] text-slate-800 min-h-screen pb-12">

    <!-- Sticky Top Navigation -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-[#EAEAEA] border-b-2 border-[#4F6D7A] px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between pointer-events-auto" style="pointer-events: auto;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="p-2 bg-white border border-[#4F6D7A]">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#4F6D7A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-lg text-[#4F6D7A] tracking-tight">GuardianAgent</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] border border-[#4F6D7A] text-[#4F6D7A] px-1.5 py-0.5 ml-2 font-mono uppercase font-bold">v1.0.0</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Center links -->
        <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-6">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors py-2 px-3 border-b-2 <%= currentPath === '/dashboard' ? 'border-[#DD6E42] text-[#4F6D7A]' : 'border-transparent text-[#4F6D7A]/60 hover:text-[#4F6D7A]' %>">
                Review Dashboard
            </a>
            <a href="/setup/github" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors py-2 px-3 border-b-2 <%= currentPath === '/setup/github' ? 'border-[#DD6E42] text-[#4F6D7A]' : 'border-transparent text-[#4F6D7A]/60 hover:text-[#4F6D7A]' %>">
                GitHub Setup
            </a>
            <a href="/setup/gitlab" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors py-2 px-3 border-b-2 <%= currentPath === '/setup/gitlab' ? 'border-[#DD6E42] text-[#4F6D7A]' : 'border-transparent text-[#4F6D7A]/60 hover:text-[#4F6D7A]' %>">
                GitLab Setup
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="text-right hidden sm:block">
                <p class="text-[10px] text-[#4F6D7A]/60 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">User</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-[#4F6D7A]"><%= userEmail %></p>
            </div>
            <a href="/logout" class="py-2 px-3 border border-[#4F6D7A] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#4F6D7A] hover:bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 transition-colors" title="Logout">
                Logout
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <div class="border border-[#4F6D7A] bg-white p-8 mb-8">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">GitHub Actions Setup Guide</h1>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mb-6 font-medium">Follow these steps to connect your GitHub repositories to GuardianAgent.</p>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <!-- Section 1 -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#4F6D7A] border-b border-[#4F6D7A]/30 pb-1.5 mb-3">1. Obtain Access Tokens</h2>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-950 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                        <li>Go to your GitHub Settings, select <strong>Developer Settings</strong> in the left sidebar, and click <strong>Personal Access Tokens (Classic)</strong>. Do not use fine-grained tokens as they require complex manual repository permission configurations.</li>
                        <li>Click <strong>Generate new token (Classic)</strong>, give the token a descriptive name, and explicitly check the <strong><code>repo</code></strong> checkbox scope to grant full repository write, commit, and pull request access.</li>
                        <li>Copy the generated token immediately. Store it securely; it will not be displayed again.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

                <!-- Section 2 -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#4F6D7A] border-b border-[#4F6D7A]/30 pb-1.5 mb-3">2. Add Secrets to GitHub</h2>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-950 font-medium leading-relaxed" start="4">
                        <li>In your GitHub repository, click <strong>Settings</strong>, then select <strong>Secrets and variables</strong> and click <strong>Actions</strong> in the sidebar.</li>
                        <li>Create a new Repository Secret (do not use Environment Secrets) named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">OPENROUTER_API_KEY</code> and paste your OpenRouter key.</li>
                        <li>Create a new Repository Secret (do not use Environment Secrets) named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">GIT_TOKEN</code> and paste your GitHub Personal Access Token (Classic).</li>
                        <li>Create a new Repository Secret (do not use Environment Secrets) named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">GUARDIAN_USER_ID</code> and paste your unique ID shown below:</li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-between border border-[#4F6D7A] bg-[#C0D6DF]/10 p-3 font-mono text-xs">
                        <span>GUARDIAN_USER_ID: <strong class="text-[#DD6E42]"><%= guardianUserId %></strong></span>
                        <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('<%= guardianUserId %>'); alert('Copied User ID!');" 
                                class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#4F6D7A] text-white hover:bg-[#4F6D7A]/90 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer">
                            Copy
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Section 3 -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#4F6D7A] border-b border-[#4F6D7A]/30 pb-1.5 mb-3">3. Create Workflow File</h2>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-950 font-medium leading-relaxed" start="8">
                        <li>In your local project, create a folder structure named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">.github/workflows</code>.</li>
                        <li>Create a new file inside named <code class="bg-[#C0D6DF]/30 px-1 font-mono text-[#4F6D7A]">guardian.yml</code>.</li>
                        <li>Copy the entire configuration snippet below, paste it into the file, commit, and push it to GitHub.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="mt-4 relative border border-[#4F6D7A] bg-[#FFFFFF]">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#4F6D7A] bg-[#C0D6DF]/15 px-4 py-2.5 text-xs font-bold text-[#4F6D7A] uppercase tracking-wider">
                            <span>GitHub Actions Workflow</span>
                            <button onclick="copySnippet()" 
                                    class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#DD6E42] hover:bg-[#DD6E42]/90 text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer transition-colors">
                                Copy Snippet
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-b border-[#4F6D7A]/20 bg-[#F5F5F5] px-4 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500">
                            Path: .github/workflows/guardian.yml
                        </div>
                        <pre id="yamlSnippet" class="p-4 font-mono text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-slate-950 overflow-x-auto max-h-[350px] bg-slate-50/50">name: Security Guardian Scan
on:
  pull_request:
    branches: [ main, master ]
jobs:
  guardian_scan:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout Code
        uses: actions/checkout@v3
        with:
          fetch-depth: 0
      - name: Setup Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v4
        with:
          python-version: '3.10'
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: |
          python -m pip install --upgrade pip
          pip install requests
      - name: Run Guardian
        env:
          OPENROUTER_API_KEY: ${{ secrets.OPENROUTER_API_KEY }}
          GIT_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.GIT_TOKEN }}
          GUARDIAN_USER_ID: "<%= guardianUserId %>"
        run: |
          curl -sS https://raw.githubusercontent.com/soft-hive-group/guardianagent-autonomous-gitlab-security-orchestrator/main/guardian.py -o guardian.py
          python guardian.py --project-id ${{ github.repository }} --mr-iid ${{ github.event.pull_request.number }}</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Troubleshooting Tips -->
                <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[#4F6D7A]/30">
                    <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#4F6D7A] mb-3">Troubleshooting Tips</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2.5 text-xs text-slate-950 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        <li><strong>Variable Spelling:</strong> Ensure all secret names are in ALL CAPS with no leading/trailing spaces.</li>
                        <li><strong>Permissions Check:</strong> If you encounter a 403 error, your token lacks write access. Ensure the token has repository write permissions.</li>
                        <li><strong>Protected Branches:</strong> For GitLab, ensure 'Protect variable' is DISABLED so the Guardian can run on your active Merge Request branches.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        function copySnippet() {
            const code = document.getElementById('yamlSnippet').innerText;
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(code).then(() => {
                alert('YAML snippet copied to clipboard!');
            }).catch(err => {
                console.error('Copy failed: ', err);
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
